{"type": "article", "id": 14718, "title": "3D打印鞋跟", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-10T06:49:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000322vxDw4U7idb1XcZtu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t3D 打印技术的兴起帮助产品实现定制，也出现了越来越多的概念产品。美国设计师 Francis Bitonti 为荷兰品牌 United Nude 打造一系列的鞋，拥有金色的 3D 鞋跟。经过电脑的严密演算，得以做成如此夸张的造型。鞋面依然是黑色皮革，所以穿上与普通的鞋并无多少差别。这一系列产品正在 United Nude 旗舰店展出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142207WA4wxPhDaNIbqT6B.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"377\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142207nb0cfOJRedHEuv9w.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261422085yG7f3kl1naBQ6we.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}